== Overview ==
Combining sub-atomic superheating of alloys into a spongy goo and a supersonic magnetic rail launching mechanism, the Federates have managed to couple together a basic Plasma weapon capable of devouring shields and consuming the armor beneath.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Plasma Cannon can be bought in the workshop after acquiring [[Plasma Technology]].
